sequenceDiagram
    participant K as kubelet
    participant CSI as CSI Driver
    participant SM as Secret Manager
    participant Sync as Sync Controller
    participant Pod as Container

    K->>CSI: mount volume (blocks)
    CSI->>SM: fetch secret
    SM-->>CSI: secret value
    CSI-->>K: mount ready<br/>(file at /mnt/secrets/...)
    Note over K,CSI: Synchronous — always done before container starts

    par
        K->>Pod: start container
        Note over Pod: Reads env var<br/>from K8s Secret
    and
        CSI-->>Sync: SPC pod status updated
        Sync->>Sync: create/update<br/>K8s Secret
    end

    Note over Pod,Sync: ⚠️ Race: container may start BEFORE<br/>K8s Secret is synced
    Pod-->>Pod: env var empty<br/>→ DB connection fails<br/>→ CrashLoopBackOff
